response.original_title: Chikara Two Eyebrows Are Better Than One
response.overview: January 27th, 2008 :: Season 7 premieres with UltraMantis Black's returns to action! The former "Equinox," Vin Gerard, looks to take his frustrations out on Worker Ant. The other members of The Colony meet perennial rivals, F.I.S.T.! The Wrestle Factory head trainers join forces with the latest graduates when Claudio Castagnoli, Lince Dorado, and Ophidian take on Mike Quackenbush, Tim Donst and Amasis. Matches featured:  1. The Order of the Neo Solar Temple vs Cheech and Cloudy  2. Moravian Greyhound vs Zombie Plantain vs Hydra  3. Vin Gerard vs Worker Ant  4. Kylie Pierce vs Sara Del Rey  5. Eddie Kingston vs Shane Storm  6. Jimmy Olsen vs Sabian  7. F.I.S.T. vs The Colony  8. Larry Sweeney vs Hallowicked  9. Claudio Castagnoli, Lince Dorado & Ophidian vs Mike Quackenbush, Amasis & Tim Donst
response.title: Chikara Two Eyebrows Are Better Than One
